Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=10}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.43,0:01:57.26,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,Até agora, um jogador foi eliminado\Ndo jogo de sobrevivência do Upper Yard,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.26,0:01:59.35,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,e oitenta permanecem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.56,0:02:04.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Devem ter faltado\Na proteção divina de Deus...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:11.03,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,Enquanto isso, quatro dos Chapéu de Palha\Npartiram em busca de ouro.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:16.53,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu objetivo: o tesouro nas\Nruínas de uma cidade antiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:21.16,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,Eles vão direto pro sul\Na partir do altar de sacrifício.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:24.71,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,Direto...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:27.13,Narrator-207-,,0,0,0,,pro sul...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.76,0:02:37.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,A floresta ficou bem movimentada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.26,0:02:40.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa casa fica longe da cidade,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,então naturalmente a floresta a engoliu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:47.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Será que as ruínas da cidade\Nem si estão em melhor estado...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:56.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mulher!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.28,0:02:59.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa rota leva ao Santuário de Deus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:02.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ir além seria saacrilégio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:05.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desça daí!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:11.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}O que é sacrilégio é você não perceber\No valor histórico dessas ruínas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.30,0:03:13.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que insolência!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você tem assunto comigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:16.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que você quer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:21.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Simples! Por mandaato de Deus,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:23.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,devo picar os Shandian\Ne vocês, povo do Blue Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:27.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,em pedacinhos com esse diaal de machado!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.86,0:03:31.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Seis Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Twist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:44.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que barbaridade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:51.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Me tira daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.34,0:03:53.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De jeito nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Para de seguir! Me solta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:16.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Shandian!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:19.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Monges guerreiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:41.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.35,0:04:46.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca devia ter vindo aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso vai te ensinar, monge guerreiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.28,0:05:02.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Muitos dos nossos aliados caíram!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:03.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses monges guerreiros são problemáticos!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Direita. Direita. Direita...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele é um dos povo do Blue Sea\Nque o Wyper mencionou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:14.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele deve ser eliminado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:19.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um guerrilheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que quer briga!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:24.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Morra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:27.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não sei qual é o problema, mas...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:35.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabo é o problema de vocês?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor, me perdoe! Eu desisto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu desisto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu perdi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por favor, me pouupe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mais um?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei, você!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se não é um sacerdote,\Nentão não me ataca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não tenho tempo pra isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.07,0:06:24.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.91,0:06:27.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que diabo são aquelas\Npistolas brilhantes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:30.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde ele foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você é bem forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe. Subestimei você,\Npessoa do Blue Sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.44,0:07:04.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não. Eu que devo me desculpar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.40,0:07:07.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tinha certeza que você era só um lacaio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.51,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele nem mexeu os pés!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:33.22,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Disseram que tem vários tipos de wavers...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:37.19,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Essas coisas de patins\Nsão só mais um tipo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.11,0:07:41.44,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele tá usando rajadas pra se impulsionar!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.32,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,E...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.32,0:07:45.78,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,as pistolas dele brilham a cada tiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.24,0:07:49.07,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Por causa delas, não consigo\Nmanter os olhos nele!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:52.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pra onde ele foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:58.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}Tiger...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.67,0:08:00.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Três espadas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:01.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}...Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:24.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um espadachim do Blue Sea que não\Nconsegue usar wavers nem dials...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.48,0:08:26.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você não tem chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:31.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sabe o que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:32.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Milky Dial!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:44.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Combate aéreo não é só\Npular desesperadamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,U-Uma enguia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:03.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa provavelmente ficaria\Nbem boa grelhada...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:26.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Eu fiz besteira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sou idiota?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.13,0:09:33.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como se já não bastasse\Na dificuldade com esse desgraçado...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:35.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,ainda levei um tiro na perna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:40.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que posso fazer sobre\Naquelas pistolas cegantes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:45.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que armas chiques\Nvocê tem aí!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas que pena!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:53.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha! Eu tenho óculos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:58.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Suas pistolas brilhantes\Nnão funcionam mais em mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então não tem sentido continuar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não parecem\Nóculos de sol pra mim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:05.75,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele percebeu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:09.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você não parece gostar\Ndas minhas flash guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Combate corpo a corpo é vital pra espadachins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você não é páreo pra mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:18.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não sei o que\Nvocês vieram fazer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:25.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas você é nosso inimigo\Nenquanto ficar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora morra de uma vez!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:30.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esse ferimento parece doloroso, afinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:32.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Guarde sua simpatia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:34.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você só raspou minha perna.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:41.37,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Me distrair com comida\Nprova que ainda me falta determinação.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:46.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa é a situação perfeita\Npra testar aquela técnica...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:49.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Devo tentar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.36,0:11:12.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fugindo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.61,0:11:19.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olhos, ouvidos, nariz,\Nlíngua, corpo, mente...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:24.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essas são as seis raízes do homem\Nque contêm o bem, o mal e a paz.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:26.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do que você tá falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E cada uma delas é\Npura ou impura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:33.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Trinta e seis desejos\Nmundanos numa vida...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.67,0:11:40.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Agora eu tenho o cano\Nde um canhão apontado pra você.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.35,0:11:43.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Suas pistolas contra meu canhão...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:46.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Em alcance e poder,\Nminha arma é superior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:48.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você se saiu bem até agora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas acaba aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:58.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um canhão?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.66,0:12:00.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você enlouqueceu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde está essa arma sua?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você já viu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,um corte voador?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.21,0:12:09.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Besteira!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.09,0:12:12.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Estilo de Uma Espada:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.39,0:12:23.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Fênix de Trinta e Seis Libras!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:42.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:46.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nada pessoal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:50.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,mas você não pode me dizer\Nquando desistir e morrer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.38,0:12:56.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou fazer o que for preciso pra sobreviver.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:24.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:30.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou completamente perdido...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:32.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.54,0:13:35.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Zoro! Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:40.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou ser deixado aqui pra morrer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.42,0:13:43.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Renas vão pro céu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O doutor vai estar me esperando lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.18,0:13:50.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não, não posso pensar assim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sou médico!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:56.02,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não posso pensar na morte tão casualmente!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:00.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas como será o céu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera, aqui não é o céu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.83,0:14:09.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou cercado de ruínas\Nde repente.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Talvez todos tenham chegado aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acho que eu sou realmente incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.92,0:14:17.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah! Será que sou o primeiro a chegar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.04,0:14:17.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Meu nariz deve ter ajudado!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:24.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eba! Sou o primeiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:27.43,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,Um tanuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:42.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pode atirar o quanto quiser, é inútil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:46.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Canhões e armas não funcionam em mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aparentemente não.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:51.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vamos tentar uma abordagem diferente.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:03.97,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que cheiro é esse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:06.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa arma é conhecida\Ncomo burn bazooka,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:10.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,que abriga um breath dial\Ncheio de gás.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.39,0:15:15.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O gás expelido se incendeia em\Nchamas azuis que queimam a presa toda!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:34.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:36.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Atravessou aquela árvore enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele sumiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:52.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:54.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:05.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\t(2563,0,1,\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)\fad(150,0)}Gomu Gomu no Stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.74,0:16:53.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se é uma bazooka que você quer,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:55.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,é uma bazooka que vai ter!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:57.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gomu Gomu no...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.75,0:17:01.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Burn...
Comment: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– ...Bazooka!\N– ...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:08.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}– ...Bazooka!\N– ...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:28.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aquele desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:41.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.71,0:17:50.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Sanji!\N– E-Ei!
Comment: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.51,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Fala alguma coisa, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:02.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.64,0:18:04.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que tá acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.53,0:18:15.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ei! Não ouço batimento cardíaco!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.12,0:18:16.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que homem tolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:29.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E eu nem vim\Ncom más intenções.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.30,0:18:34.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então por que você tá aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:38.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que recepção fria...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.23,0:18:47.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Realmente foram seis longos anos,\Nantigo deus Gan Fall...
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=11}===============================DIALOGUE============================
